Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.72,0:00:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,A bit more lively...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.81,0:00:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,SCHEDULE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.06,0:00:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe the tempo should be a little higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.15,0:00:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.98,0:00:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The drums set the tone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.19,0:00:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The melody stirs up your feelings, and the lyrics just flow by themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That moment when everything sounds perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.92,0:00:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That euphoric feeling that puts us on cloud nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.84,0:00:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Already midnight.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, hold up, what?\NWhat the heck am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.18,0:01:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to study, darn it! Study!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.90,0:01:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just layering them isn't gonna cut it, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.03,0:01:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Then maybe I should try to tone down the intensity on this one a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.21,0:01:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,STUDYING!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.60,0:03:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,A SLAPSTICK Q&A SESSION
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.94,0:03:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The pigeon was on the rhythm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't even finished 2 pages since yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point I might as well have just played around all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Some guitar.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, there was an acoustic one too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Nina-chan, come on in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you eaten already?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.72,0:03:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a meat bun? They're great!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.48,0:03:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's bad manners!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, you're definitely a rich girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.11,0:03:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Sauce on meat buns?...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.03,0:04:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me, they're better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.78,0:04:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend gave me those as leftovers from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.99,0:04:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.37,0:04:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.71,0:04:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Great. Glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.01,0:04:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what about that song? You finish it yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.13,0:04:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Would be nice if you could\Nactually do it that quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you call us here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I live pretty far from here you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.14,0:04:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought we should talk about\Nwhat kind of song it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.31,0:04:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, I can't see it right now.\NWhat the three of us should sound like.?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.69,0:04:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm fine with anything as long as I'm on drums.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.94,0:04:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.28,0:04:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I showed you this app like, what, a week ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And you can already make something like this?\NAwesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.01,0:05:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that... Momoka told me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I could compose without knowing music theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.76,0:05:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I gave it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, for the result to be this good,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you must've been at it for at least\N8 hours a day, haven't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.53,0:05:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to study! I HAVE TO STUDY!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, I hit the nail on the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the one who showed me the app,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.87,0:05:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah no, this is all on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.67,0:05:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you know then quit taking it out on others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.51,0:05:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have shown you that app.\NHere, let me just uninstall it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.84,0:05:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.97,0:05:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.35,0:05:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need to get myself together,\Nand leave the rest of the band stuff to you. Easy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you even talking to?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.65,0:06:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,To myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, see you next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.36,0:06:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is up with this girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.24,0:06:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be heading back too then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold up, there's a ton of meat buns left!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have them. Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.75,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna go together?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.51,0:06:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.84,0:06:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty amazing, you know.\NComposing a song all by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.85,0:06:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I definitely wouldn't be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I just...looked up some guides and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.35,0:06:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I definitely wouldn't have been\Nable to write lyrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.03,0:06:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.61,0:06:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, sorry, I have to stop by\Nthe convenience store...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.87,0:06:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was planning to walk back home right after...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.92,0:07:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Later then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.27,0:07:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru too, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go there your-\NI mean, couldn't you go there yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.61,0:07:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't, got a shift later.\NYou got something to do too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.11,0:07:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, you can go after class.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just take it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.54,0:07:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She gave you meat buns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.21,0:07:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that famous place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.09,0:07:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Country bumpkin spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.80,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Which way is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:07:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.77,0:08:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.44,0:08:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.20,0:08:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.04,0:08:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.25,0:08:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Awa-san around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.00,0:08:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Awa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Subaru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.09,0:08:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru, over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think the play's fine as is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.27,0:08:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have trouble getting here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I could have come to meet you,\nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for taking so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.44,0:08:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.65,0:08:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,My savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget your phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.28,0:08:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I did an oopsie~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:08:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- Okay.\N- See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,See you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have time after this?\NWant to grab a bite to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,My treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I, uh, have to study...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.55,0:09:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. How about the weekend then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.59,0:09:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, on Sunday?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.64,0:09:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, you don't have to...\NIt's just a small favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.93,0:09:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm gonna go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.10,0:09:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm talking about the band.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not stupid, you know.\nI can see that you're avoiding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.41,0:09:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not trying\nto get in your way or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,There are other bands.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're wrong.\NIt's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.21,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.30,0:09:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.09,0:09:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.68,0:10:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's fine.\nI can always study later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I study at my own pace anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.48,0:10:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that, I mean about myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I started music in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So I definitely can't say\NI know everything, but
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.94,0:10:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,since the members of a band always\Ncreate something together,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,they're usually pretty tight-knit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,If disagreements come up, bottling it up won't work.\N
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting up a facade is just going to\Nlead to problems down the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.33,0:10:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So if something bothers you,\nyou better speak up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.42,0:10:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I have nothing against you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.55,0:10:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all my fault in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,See, this is what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.26,0:10:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,People usually end up hating me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Argh, no, that's not what I mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that, I usually distance myself from people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.44,0:10:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shy, so it always feels like they're just\Nforcing themselves to talk to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you hate it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.03,0:10:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly hate, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.40,0:11:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know, when people are friendly with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help but think something like\N"Don't think it'll go your way, I'm not that easy!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.83,0:11:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,at some point...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.62,0:11:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.12,0:11:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm guessing that's why you dropped out of high school?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.46,0:11:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... did she tell you about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:22.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You really like playing the good guy, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.93,0:11:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, listen you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're completely wrong about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm going to acting school,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not like a regular school\Nthat lets you take college exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the same boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, but you want to be an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That means you're pursuing a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.36,0:11:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,At least you have something to tell others!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.16,0:11:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's where you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.92,0:11:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Her face looks familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.25,0:11:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mémé's Investigations{\i0}.\nRebroadcast every noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.21,0:12:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.42,0:12:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a huge pain, you know.\N"You have to follow in my footsteps", and all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.22,0:12:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,She's the one who arranged\Nfor me to be sent to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you want to become an actress?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.19,0:12:17.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're still going to acting school?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.15,0:12:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And I hate myself for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't even want it, so what the heck am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.03,0:12:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one around me knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.78,0:12:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone thinks I'm naturally\Ntrying to carry on the family tradition.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.46,0:12:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why did you join a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my way of quietly protesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In middle school, I was really against joining the theater club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.59,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So since I like bands, I ended up joining the Light Music Club.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.84,0:12:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a blast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I even played in bands without telling anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.10,0:12:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So your grandmother didn't know at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like I could tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, have you seen the Hachiko statue?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:56.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't people think we're country bumpkins?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So what? You are one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.44,0:13:01.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, think of it as thanks for listening to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.28,0:13:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not getting rid of me from today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.78,0:13:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Girls Band Cry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SUNDAY NOON
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.74,0:13:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A street performance?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it would be a good start.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already booked a place for this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.17,0:13:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't we supposed to start by recording\Na song and uploading a video?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.51,0:13:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still on the agenda.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.30,0:13:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But something tells me we need to get started quickly,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,- especially with our lineup.\N- A concert, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.85,0:13:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking at the photo you sent me back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You two were radiating an aura of misfortune and frustration.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.06,0:13:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,- Rude.\N- Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's exactly why I thought
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd be good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,- What do you think, Nina?\N- I'm not exactly happy about it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.45,0:13:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.91,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we can play without a bassist?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.21,0:13:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina can't play any instruments, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Relax, it's a place for amateurs.\NWe'll manage somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.92,0:14:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, we have this thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.38,0:14:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.42,0:14:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,A looper.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To record a musical loop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.02,0:14:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I just realized something\Nabout street performances...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.23,0:14:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Does the "street" part mean\Nwe'll perform {\\i1}in front of people{\\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, duh.\NAnd besides, you've already seen me in action.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,- Where are you going?\N- I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone! That wasn't the plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Pull yourself together.\NYou sang at the station, remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.59,0:14:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.92,0:14:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Easier said than done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any experience with that stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, if anything goes wrong I'll make it work somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.47,0:14:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you sing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.02,0:14:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way better than me anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And you'll play the guitar?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.81,0:15:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.61,0:15:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, I want you behind the microphone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll understand when you sing. Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're leaving the band too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly. Thanks and good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, wait-
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.88,0:15:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.60,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being unfair, putting us on the spot like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.73,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not making sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,- But I-\N- Stop freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.86,0:15:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether it goes well or not,\Nwhether you fail or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll have regrets either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.86,0:15:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,- You don't know that...\N- You know I'm right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.87,0:15:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me, you have everything to gain,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.66,0:16:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,by baring your soul and singing everything\Nthat's boiling up inside you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.37,0:16:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.83,0:16:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, you lost this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.25,0:16:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this attitude of yours and put it into the song!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,That will be the real you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.85,0:16:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Their equipment's pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. They're the cheapest place around here though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.27,0:16:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, this'll do.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina, do you have the lyrics memorized?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.20,0:16:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to fit in a bit of your composing too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.67,0:16:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's give it a shot then.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.38,0:16:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think we came here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You caught me off guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, stop freaking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a rehearsal, it's bound to be bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.22,0:16:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll definitely mess up somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:16:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.78,0:17:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.72,0:17:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One, two, three, four.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.86,0:17:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It totally gave me chills.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.74,0:18:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I got goosebumps all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.87,0:18:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.08,0:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You fell right into Momoka-san's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.62,0:18:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you feel that, there's no turning back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.50,0:18:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,can't help but move to the beat of a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.80,0:18:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance and music are in our DNA.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.89,0:18:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.35,0:18:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.68,0:18:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, I was just thinking\Nyou really do have an amazing voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.10,0:18:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it gave me chills too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.86,0:18:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's try singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.94,0:18:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A medium with a beer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.65,0:18:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,A medium, no onions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.28,0:18:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Medium for me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.58,0:18:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah, who's this raspy old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.20,0:18:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't have told me to sing at the top of my lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think anyone could actually get to this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.21,0:18:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.67,0:18:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thank you so much."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:19:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, your voice should be back tomorrow.\NBe careful with your throat though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a band?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.26,0:19:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The guitar case caught my attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Come see us, if you feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.73,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SHIN-KAWASAKI (PROVISIONAL)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.90,0:19:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Look what I got.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.61,0:19:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we could give them ours too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.12,0:19:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's wait until we hear them sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.24,0:19:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for the meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.16,0:19:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Go where?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.08,0:19:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,To work.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.17,0:19:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She treated us today too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.22,0:19:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Paid both for the venue and the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is she looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.35,0:19:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Her former bandmates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.10,0:19:53.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Those four.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.86,0:20:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Let's welcome the very first performance of a brand new band!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A girls' trio straight from Kawasaki!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.53,0:20:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Make some noise for...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.58,0:20:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Shin-Kawasaki"?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:17.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm calling a meeting on the subject\N of our band name later.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told you, it's temporary...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.26,0:20:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry I'm late.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.10,0:20:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}{\i1}Wait a second...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't tell me that's your stage outfit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it bad?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.39,0:20:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I told you, you have to bare your soul.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.31,0:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go change.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.49,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Testing testing 1 2 3...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.24,0:20:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You need an outfit you would definitely hate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.74,0:20:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't overthink it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.50,0:20:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have to let your emotions flow freely.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't worry, you're not alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.67,0:20:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're shy, but stubborn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.13,0:21:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cowardly, but full of confidence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A true walking paradox.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.01,0:21:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Nina! We're up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:15.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've accumulated so much anger and energy within you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And that...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.19,0:21:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}is what we call rock.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.86,0:21:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Nina Iseri: Rina\nMomoka Kawaragi: Yûri
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Subaru Awa: Mirei
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.04,0:21:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No one knows you. No one cares about you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.13,0:21:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that's what makes it all so thrilling.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're rock'n'roll, Nina.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.74,0:22:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If nothing changes, no matter the wait{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.66,0:22:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then I see no common ground{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Blaming someone is never enough\NTo heal the wounds{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.87,0:22:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to say goodbye\NTo those long days{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.63,0:22:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I spent curled up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.09,0:22:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not like I believe\Nin any deity{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Shut up\N{\i0}- {\i1}Shut up{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.64,0:22:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- {\i1}Leave me alone\N{\i0}- {\i1}Leave me alone{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A stranger singing\Nuntil losing her voice{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.73,0:22:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promises me\Nthat nothing is an end in itself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.19,0:22:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Perhaps these banalities\NResonated in some hearts{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.44,0:22:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't know{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.24,0:22:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.57,0:22:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh really?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I forgot{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.03,0:22:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm tired{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.20,0:22:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to break everything{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.49,0:22:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My courage has left me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.50,0:23:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For pity's sake, someone give me\Na reason to exist{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.13,0:23:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Replacements,\Nthere are too many to count{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.42,0:23:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Easy to order me to be myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.72,0:23:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These words sound\Nlike a staged performance{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.64,0:23:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dreaming to see reality\Ncatch up with us{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.35,0:23:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is there anyone at all?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.91,0:23:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is...awesome...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.21,0:23:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is rock'n'roll!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I'M LEAVING THE GROUP, SORRY!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.63,0:23:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\i1}Next time:\N"Gratitude and Surprise".{\i0}
